#: 2020-07-30-lockdown-emissions.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "What’s Polluting Our Air in the First Place?"
msgstr "Co zanieczyszcza nasze powietrze?"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-30-lockdown-emissions.md:31
